{"tid":2046464,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"傳中國停購部分美國大豆、豬肉　中美貿易協議受考驗","createTime":"2020-06-01T12:08:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T12:47:54.000Z","uid":66271,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"502539c722bb3cee302ecb84b07c1fe42e0b9ce6","tid":2046464,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:08:15.000Z","msg":"《彭博》引述知情人士透露，中國政府已指示國有農產品商貿公司暫停進口美國農產品，包括大豆。<br />\n<br />\n知情人士稱，暫時只有國有貿易商中糧和中儲糧接到暫停進口的指示，民營公司尚未接收到暫停進口的命令。<br />\n<br />\n除了大豆等農產品外，更傳中國買家取消部分美國豬肉訂單。<br />\n<br />\n消息傳出後，大豆期貨短線大幅回落，日內升幅接近悉數蒸發，其後喘定回穩。美股三大指數期貨更轉升為跌，道指期貨下跌約100點，標普期貨亦跌近0.5%。"},{"pid":"38e3e85b7aba00e90d66945c2e5c4555eda1dae0","tid":2046464,"uid":193072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:09:12.000Z","msg":"又違約"},{"pid":"2fbad34b1ac04ec672b338e498054fb7b74cb284","tid":2046464,"uid":83228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:09:19.000Z","msg":"傻啦 巴西會夾你做傻仔"},{"pid":"7ab96c1284c44217e647383d691ad2b02b78b141","tid":2046464,"uid":134522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:09:55.000Z","msg":"好！支持中國！"},{"pid":"c25ac63682c58df2fc66bdf35c4f409315ab7570","tid":2046464,"uid":352873,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:12:02.000Z","msg":"冇錢買 想毁約"},{"pid":"25ceb4dfb8ac06337ed66070c9a7c546a9baa7c3","tid":2046464,"uid":170297,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:13:24.000Z","msg":"無錢買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e24c94479c882d0a077799b21faa8d33474a6f","tid":2046464,"uid":88982,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:28:09.000Z","msg":"好好奇 到底美國d農場咩心情<br />\n比支那咁撚狗法"},{"pid":"8746f316826a2f9d4992dad9052be9cc12303885","tid":2046464,"uid":12599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:35:04.000Z","msg":"有咩考驗，唔係全世界都知支國係想拖時間先簽？<br />\n<br />\n真係有真心膠覺得中國會實行到d條款？"},{"pid":"3d8c864